%N A393907 Number of planar embedding isomorphism classes of the n-Hanoi graph.
%C A393907 These counts allow the mirror image as an isomorphism.
%H A393907 Andrew Howroyd, <a href="/A393907/b393907.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..500</a>
%H A393907 Eric Weisstein's World of Mathematics, <a href="https://mathworld.wolfram.com/HanoiGraph.html">Hanoi Graph</a>.
%H A393907 Eric Weisstein's World of Mathematics, <a href="https://mathworld.wolfram.com/PlanarEmbedding.html">Planar Embedding</a>.
%H A393907 <a href="/index/Rec#order_03">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (14,-56,64).
%F A393907 From _Andrew Howroyd_, Mar 02 2026: (Start)
%F A393907 a(n) = (8^(n-1) + 2*2^(n-1) + 3*4^(n-1))/12 for n > 1.
%F A393907 G.f.: x*(1 - 12*x + 38*x^2 - 32*x^3)/((1 - 2*x)*(1 - 4*x)*(1 - 8*x)). (End)
%t A393907 A393907[n_] := If[n == 1, 1, 2^(n-5)*(2^n+2)*(2^n+4)/3]; Array[A393907, 25] (* or *)
%t A393907 LinearRecurrence[{14, -56, 64}, {1, 2, 10, 60}, 25] (* _Paolo Xausa_, Mar 03 2026 *)
%o A393907 (PARI) a(n) = if(n==1, 1, (8^(n-1) + 2*2^(n-1) + 3*4^(n-1))/12) \\ _Andrew Howroyd_, Mar 02 2026
